{"tid":965596,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"SM娛樂內地團「威神V」與NCT劃清界線？　Lucas黃旭熙備受重視","createTime":"2019-01-02T07:28:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-04T05:19:36.000Z","uid":3189,"like":6,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"762b567b4508451896ba899886071f5925a009f6","tid":965596,"uid":3189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T07:28:56.000Z","msg":"韓國男團NCT曾宣布於今年下半年推出中國小分隊，惟NCTzen（NCT歌迷）一直只聞樓梯響，NCT中國小分隊遲遲未正式公開露面。終於，在2018年最後一天，SM娛樂宣布NCT成員黃旭熙Lucas、錕、Ten、Winwin，還有SM Rookies的肖俊、Hendery和揚揚將會在2019年1月以組合「威神V（WayV）」名義在中國內地出道。七位均來自中國，或者是華裔成員。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2270746/org/9a912c83e84a01753503befb9615901b.jpg/R0ywxWZlWNfdnc0mhNkQZAGLUkJ1Sm3wC5LtdguS7XY?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2270746%2Forg%2F9a912c83e84a01753503befb9615901b.jpg%2FR0ywxWZlWNfdnc0mhNkQZAGLUkJ1Sm3wC5LtdguS7XY%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=4a59db4d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nNCT曾預告會在今年內推出中國小分隊，不過粉絲沒想到要等到12月31日才正式公布新小分隊消息。（網上圖片）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n雖然威神V是SM娛樂旗下組合，不過在其官方微博簡介是「Label V旗下男子组合」，未有言明與SM娛樂的關係，此外，SM娛樂的官方微博亦只讚好了威神V的出道帖文，未有轉發宣傳，加上威神V的組合名稱沒有寫明是NCT的小分隊。從種種跡象可見，SM娛樂可能為免威神V受內地限韓令影響，所以索性將威神V塑造成全新內地男團，而非NCT中國小分隊。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2270745/org/0745edc8efec15be8367f4234f320644.jpg/nHAT_T1LnttQZaKJLzDTuBnJeD6qThDjucD8e7nA_Hs?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2270745%2Forg%2F0745edc8efec15be8367f4234f320644.jpg%2FnHAT_T1LnttQZaKJLzDTuBnJeD6qThDjucD8e7nA_Hs%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=cb62bdfa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n雖然威神V屬SM娛樂旗下組合，但SM娛樂僅讚好威神V微博，並沒有轉發宣傳。（網上截圖）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2270747/org/74c807e1e2def543ffa496344663a883.jpg/FFLg6TpVW99iVCarpHiOgAIVDk4ecFS85lV7kOZVe5A?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2270747%2Forg%2F74c807e1e2def543ffa496344663a883.jpg%2FFFLg6TpVW99iVCarpHiOgAIVDk4ecFS85lV7kOZVe5A%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=0c2f8c80&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nSM娛樂雖然沒有在微博宣傳新團，仍有在Facebook發布威神V的消息。（網上截圖）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n威神V的官方照片中，香港成員黃旭熙Lucas站在正中間，可見近日在韓國和其他亞洲地區人氣急升的Lucas受到SM娛樂的重神。威神V預告將於北京時間2019年1月1日凌晨12時正發布首條預告片，屆時一眾NCTzen和其他K-pop粉絲可以欣賞威神V的片段迎接新一年來臨。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/AoLoCtFlK-k\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FAoLoCtFlK-k&d=cFyyBEaL9oyRSxvD5eL3%2BwtTNu1qqkxUxYmVHECffP4%3D&h=a43e3dac\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/AoLoCtFlK-k</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/sAiqhaBXQqc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FsAiqhaBXQqc&d=cFyyBEaL9oyRSxvD5eL3%2BwtTNu1qqkxUxYmVHECffP4%3D&h=de2653a9\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/sAiqhaBXQqc</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E5%A8%9B%E6%A8%82/277258/sm%E5%A8%9B%E6%A8%82%E5%85%A7%E5%9C%B0%E5%9C%98-%E5%A8%81%E7%A5%9Ev-%E8%88%87nct%E5%8A%83%E6%B8%85%E7%95%8C%E7%B7%9A-lucas%E9%BB%83%E6%97%AD%E7%86%99%E5%82%99%E5%8F%97%E9%87%8D%E8%A6%96\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582%25E5%25A8%259B%25E6%25A8%2582%2F277258%2Fsm%25E5%25A8%259B%25E6%25A8%2582%25E5%2585%25A7%25E5%259C%25B0%25E5%259C%2598-%25E5%25A8%2581%25E7%25A5%259Ev-%25E8%2588%2587nct%25E5%258A%2583%25E6%25B8%2585%25E7%2595%258C%25E7%25B7%259A-lucas%25E9%25BB%2583%25E6%2597%25AD%25E7%2586%2599%25E5%2582%2599%25E5%258F%2597%25E9%2587%258D%25E8%25A6%2596&d=cFyyBEaL9oyRSxvD5eL3%2BwtTNu1qqkxUxYmVHECffP4%3D&h=78d682a8\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E5%A8%9B%E6%A8%82/277258/sm%E5%A8%9B%E6%A8%82%E5%85%A7%E5%9C%B0%E5%9C%98-%E5%A8%81%E7%A5%9Ev-%E8%88%87nct%E5%8A%83%E6%B8%85%E7%95%8C%E7%B7%9A-lucas%E9%BB%83%E6%97%AD%E7%86%99%E5%82%99%E5%8F%97%E9%87%8D%E8%A6%96</a>"},{"pid":"b6053075e32710367eb6010838eee8c276e68831","tid":965596,"uid":35014,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":